author: Reuters Editorial
title: Taiwan says WHO ignored its coronavirus questions at start of outbreak
description: Taiwan accused the World Heath Organization of ignoring its questions at the start of the coronavirus outbreak, part of what it has long described as a pattern that puts it at risk because of Chinese pressure to exclude it from international bodies.
